{"tid":117822,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)ABC+偵探","createTime":"2017-02-12T13:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T19:04:54.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"828c6532a5866c6e23f2c4e4965f29573b4465c2","tid":117822,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=28a4fb37\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=be9bb6ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9a/TheDetective2007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9a%2FTheDetective2007.jpg&h=29de4c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.亞探(郭富城飾)是一潦倒的私家偵探。某日，花名肥龍(成奎安飾)的人帶著醉意拿著一張女子相片，請亞探代為找出「她」以阻止這女子想殺他的行動。亞探見有豐厚酬勞，便一口答應肥龍所託辦之事。亞探找到相片裡的士多，獲悉此女子名莫慧心(Natthasinee Pinyopiyavid飾)，是該士多的常客。<br />\n<br />\n亞探去找慧心，但見慧心家門重門深鎖。士多伙記(阿炳)拿了一名男子，大頭明的地址給亞探叫他試試。當亞探到達大頭明家門，赫然發現大頭明上吊於廳中。而在大頭明(Chaiyapong Settagarn飾)的手提電話中有數個相信是與他有染的女子相片儲存著，其中一人是燕(谷祖琳飾)，亞探從燕口中查得大頭明其中一合作夥伴素芳...<br />\n<br />\n2.陳探（郭富城飾）自從離開了警局，就成為了一名私家偵探。在他心中卻一直隱藏著一個疑惑，當年他的父母到底是怎樣去世的。他的父親到底做了什麼。但是，當他還來不及調查的時候，童年好友風澤（廖啟智飾）帶著一宗謀殺案現場的圖片出現了。那是陳探第一次看到那些照片，他驚呆了，望著眼前一幅幅血肉模糊的畫面，陳探陷入了思考之中，罪犯到底想告訴我們什麼。但是，在他來不及思考的時候，第二宗、第三宗案件接連發生。陳探深陷案情之中..<br />\n<br />\n3.繼承上集，陳探（郭富城飾）得悉其父母死於他殺後決心找出真兇，於是拿著一張照片作線索，到馬來西亞找一個叫柴哥的人。柴哥告訴探，其父母為毒販，而他們的死也和毒品有關，並透露從上波哥和輝仔身上可得到更多線索。探難以置信，他不能接受自己的父母竟為毒販。及後，探家中被人洗劫，暗格中的物件亦不翼而飛，他懷疑此物是一件相當重要的證物，並和其父母之死有密切關係。基於人生路不熟，探請來馬來西亞私家偵探鄭風喜﹙張家輝飾﹚協助調查此事..<br />\n<br />\n10 20PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956e33a17d479b8d11d7d4b5358b11aae8d8ff8a","tid":117822,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5640f6bd75887c7bcc8f1ab636d58e3ad5c6367f","tid":117822,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01477ea0186984fca052a353b53df80136d1e5e4","tid":117822,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675ffe76dc370b0165f0c6d45de610a41116a056","tid":117822,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec0a1178c86831df17f9bf35a438a01e3d8789f","tid":117822,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd800a982a32d7a2e8bd28865a8c716201c1dd7","tid":117822,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T18:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4c0d6ed0